AN Audi R8 spyder caused a multiple car accident and the driver is on the run. It’s reported that the incident happened in a Paris suburb Petit Nanterre on Sunday after the R8 and a Porsche were rented for a wedding. In one of the videos, a Mercedes Benz GLE Coupe can be seen with some damage at the back and next to a Mini Countryman, and the engine of the R8 can be seem banning on the side of the road. No one was injured in the accident. Rodéo de voiture à Nanterre cette nuit . De lourds dégâts . pic.twitter.com/zhWdmBRyDL 